<title>UK: London's IPE to close early Thursday and Friday.</title>
<headline>London's IPE to close early Thursday and Friday.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-07-02</dateline>
<text>
<p>London's International Petroleum Exchange said it will close crude futures trading early on Thursday and Friday.</p>
<p>The exchange's Brent crude contract will close at 1630 GMT (1730 local time) on July 3 and July 4.</p>
<p>The shorter hours allow for Independence Day holidays in the United States.</p>
<p>New York Mercantile Exchange energy futures contracts close early on Thursday July 3 and reopen on Monday July 7.</p>
<p>--London newsroom +44 171 542 6280</p>
